We were sitting at the marble bar area and were too embarrassed to do that thing where you pound the table so the sake drops in the beer. HOWEVER, the really nice lady that worked there noticed us not setting up the chopsticks for the sake bomb so she came over and set it up for us and we felt obligated to say the chant but obligated in the best way possible because it felt like she really wanted us to have a good time.
